You can install mongo db by 2 ways.
1) RPM way.
2) TGZ way.
You can download both things from below URL.
https://www.mongodb.com/download-center/community

You can find 5 types of packages on this site.
server  ---> RPM for mongodb
mongos  ---> Mongos required in sharding with replication setup
tools   ---> Utliity related to mongodb
shell   ---> Provide mongo shell
TGZ     ---> Above all 4 packages included in this package


